## Insert mode
Switch to normal mode|Escape
Commit undo checkpoint|Ctrl-s
Autocomplete|Ctrl-x
Insert a register content|Ctrl-r
Delete previous word|Ctrl-w / Alt-Backspace
Delete next word|Alt-d / Alt-Delete
Delete to start of line|Ctrl-u
Delete to end of line|Ctrl-k
Delete previous char|Ctrl-h / Backspace
Delete next char|Ctrl-d / Delete
Insert new line|Ctrl-j / Enter
Move to previous line|Up
Move to next line|Down
Backward a char|Left
Forward a char|Right
Move one page up|PageUp
Move one page down|PageDown
Move to line start|Home
Move to line end|End
